message.content: cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.DB. The paper discusses deep neural networks in natural language processing, which falls under the category of computational linguistics (cs.CL). The use of symbolic meaning representations and indexing for efficient retrieval suggests a possible connection to information retrieval (cs.IR) and database systems (cs.DB).
